.ti 0
Abstract

.in 3
This memo presents a technique for using Pandoc syntax as a source
format for documents in the Internet-Drafts (I-Ds) and Request for
Comments (RFC) series.

This version is adapted to work with "xml2rfc" version 2.x.

.ti 0
