.ce 2
Figure 4: This is the caption, with text in `typewriter`. Which isnt
converted to a <spanx> style, because this is copied as-is.

And how a figure that is not centered, do to using "figure" and not
"Figure".
.nf

This is a figure
This is a figure
.fi

